        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/475/125002/475_125002_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-475",
        "content": "She collects postage stamps. Such a resource.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-475_125002_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/475/125002/475_125002_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-475",
        "content": "Those people with her are the Whimples, very old acquaintances of mine; they're always having trouble, poor things.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-475_125002_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/475/125002/475_125002_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-475",
        "content": "\"Trouble is not one of those fancies you can take up and drop at any moment; it's like a grouse moor or the opium habit-once you start it you've got to keep it up.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-475_125002_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/475/125002/475_125002_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-475",
        "content": "\"Their eldest son was such a disappointment to them; they wanted him to be a linguist, and spent no end of money on having him taught to speak-oh, dozens of languages!--and then he became a Trappist monk.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-475_125002_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/475/125002/475_125002_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-475",
        "content": "And the youngest, who was intended for the American marriage market, has developed political tendencies, and writes pamphlets about the housing of the poor.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-475_125002_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/475/125002/475_125002_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-475",
        "content": "\"There are different ways of taking disappointment.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-475_125002_000022_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/475/125002/475_125002_000022_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-475",
        "content": "That's what I call being vindictive.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-475_125002_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/475/125002/475_125002_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-475",
        "content": "\"Life is full of its disappointments,\" observed the Duchess, \"and I suppose the art of being happy is to disguise them as illusions.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-475_125002_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/475/125002/475_125002_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-475",
        "content": "But that, my dear Reginald, becomes more difficult as one grows older.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-475_125002_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/475/125002/475_125002_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-475",
        "content": "\"I think it's more generally practised than you imagine.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-475_125002_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/475/125002/475_125002_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-475",
        "content": "The young have aspirations that never come to pass, the old have reminiscences of what never happened.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-475_125002_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/475/125002/475_125002_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-475",
        "content": "\"After all,\" said the Duchess, \"the disillusions of life may depend on our way of assessing it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-475_125002_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/475/125002/475_125002_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-475",
        "content": "In the minds of those who come after us we may be remembered for qualities and successes which we quite left out of the reckoning.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-475_125002_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/475/125002/475_125002_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-475",
        "content": "There may have been disillusionments in the lives of the mediaeval saints, but they would scarcely have been better pleased if they could have foreseen that their names would be associated nowadays chiefly with racehorses and the cheaper clarets.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    }
